    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a car that\u2019s got character and reliability! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its journeys, but it remains a dependable choice for your daily commute. It\u2019s been well-loved and is looking for a new home where its solid performance can truly shine. A great opportunity to own a functional ride at a fantastic price!",
