    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require a significant investment of time and money to return it to a roadworthy state. The exterior shows substantial rust along the wheel wells and rocker panels, along with several noticeable dents and faded, peeling clear coat. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there is a persistent leak in the transmission. The interior has several tears in the upholstery and the electronics are intermittent. This is being sold as-is, ideally for parts or as a major restoration project for someone with the necessary mechanical skills.",
      "price": 2800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine with no scratches, dents, or stone chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, and all interior surfaces are spotless, still retaining that new-car scent. Every electronic feature and mechanical component operates perfectly, reflecting a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in showroom state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, meticulously preserved to meet the most exacting standards. This unit exhibits a showroom-quality finish and mechanical integrity that mirrors its original production state. Curated for the discerning buyer, it offers an uncompromising aesthetic and performance profile, representing a premier acquisition for any serious collection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in incredible shape. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, never a scratch, and it still smells like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is in museum-grade condition, showing zero signs of track use or mechanical fatigue. The 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. Maintenance is current with preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator replacement already completed. The Alpine White paint retains its factory luster with no swirl marks or rock chips, while the Novillo leather interior remains supple. A true turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Flawless original paint. Pristine interior. Mechanically perfect. Full service records included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of wear, while the dashboard and trim pieces remain flawless. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete and documented service history from authorized specialists. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as intended. It drives with the tightness and precision of a new vehicle, with no rattles or road noise. Included are all original manuals, two sets of master keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved masterpiece in flawless condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
